<div class="container">
  <div class="row mt-4 justify-content-center">
    <span class="text-center font-weight-bold">
      成果を共有し、成功体験を広めるコミュニティサイト<br>
      目標達成に悩む人や人生の転換期を迎える人を対象に<br>
      効果的な目標達成をサポートする場を提供。<br>
      仕事や趣味での成果不足や新しいスキル習得の際に活用可能
    </span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 px-5 px-sm-0 mx-auto align-self-center text-start" style="margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 50px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xl-12">
        <table class="table table-hover table-inverse">
          
          
          <style>
        
          .slider {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 auto;
          }

          .slider > :first-child {
            animation: scroll 30s infinite linear;
          }
      
          @keyframes scroll {
            0% { margin-left: 0; }
            20% { margin-left: -100%; }
            50% { margin-left: -200%; }
            70% { margin-left: -300%; }
            100% { margin-left: -400%; }
          }
        </style>
        
        <body>
          <div class="slider">
            <div class="slider-item">
              <%= image_tag 'top1.jpg', style: "width: 1200px; height: 800px;" %>
            </div>
             
            <div class="slider-item">
              <%= image_tag 'top2.jpg', style: "width: 1200px; height: 800px;" %>
            </div>
             
            <div class="slider-item">
              <%= image_tag 'top3.jpeg', style: "width: 1200px; height: 800px;" %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="slider-item">
              <%= image_tag 'top4.jpeg', style: "width: 1200px; height: 800px;" %>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </body>
        
        
       </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>